Definition: the electromagnetic radiation that would be radiated from an ideal black body
Example: the distribution of energy in the radiated spectrum of a black body depends only on temperature and is determined by Planck's radiation law
Synonyms: blackbody_radiation, electromagnetic_radiation, the, electromagnetic, radiation, that, would, be, radiated, from, an, ideal, black, body, distribution, of, energy, in, spectrum, a, depends, only, on, temperature, and, is, determined, by, Planck, s, law
Category: noun.phenomenon
